Message.message: You are a herding dog and your mission is to herd.  Scare goats and push fences to fulfill your duty.
If you find yourself stuck, you can attempt a different challenge and return later.
Sheep are more sedentary than goats are.
Toggle the red switch by pressing Action (X) while adjacent to it.
Blue switches behave exactly as you would expect them to.
These sheep somehow ended up on mountains.  They are too scared to move.
Press Action (X) to rotate the shears.  In addition to herding, fill your baskets with wool by shearing all the animals.
Due to insurance regulations, animals cannot be sheared while on a mountain.
Congratulations!  All the animals are safely in their pens, and your new diploma hangs framed in the doghouse.  You are truly a Herding Hero.
